I think it's completely normal.
Some people come with a romantic vision and their head in the clouds and when they learn that they have to go two days to try, go to the preparatory test and spend a lot of time traveling and in concerts, the initial euphoria quickly leaves them.
But that’s how it works everywhere, in every group that wants to work and get something.
The Tap Tap Group currently has twenty members.
How many of them were already at the beginning of 1998?
Only one: Lađa Angelovič.
We are an open group, people enter and go out, you cannot avoid.
Whoever has will and wishes will always find the doors open
